data.description: Rare find!! This expansive two-story sits in the highly desired New Braunfels community of Stone Gate. Roof replaced in 2019. The first floor features a spacious living room centered around a beautiful brick fireplace. It opens up to the dining area and a large kitchen with tons of counter/cabinet space, and an island - perfect for entertaining! The laundry room is just off the kitchen, along with an impressive grand pantry (see the pictures!). Laminate flooring on the first floor and neutral carpet upstairs makes for easy upkeep or replacement. All bedrooms are conveniently located upstairs, including the primary suite, which boasts a walk-in closet and a double vanity in the bathroom. BONUS ROOM UPSTAIRS works perfectly as a fourth bedroom, or as an office. The fenced-in backyard includes a covered patio, a storage shed, and mature trees, making it for outdoor dining and entertainment. Live in one of the most sought-after towns in Texas, all while being just a quick drive from Downtown New Braunfels, near the Guadalupe river, and conveniently near IH-35, major retailers, dining and entertainment.
